OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Ffine end to the day, with bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Leading into a dry, warm
OL,8,Fand muggy night with variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud, clear spells and light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FEarly cloud will soon break
OL,12,Fup to give a mostly fine day with
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells. Feeling very
OL,14,Fwarm and muggy. Light winds. Chance of
OL,15,Fisolated thunderstorms by evening.
